<paragraph blockId="3.[714,1247,1578,1667]" lastBlockId="4.[151,684,1394,1483]" lastPageId="4" lastPageNumber="59" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">
This is a small delicate species of dark and humid forests at low elevation, found once in 
<collectingCountry box="[714,860,1641,1667]" name="Madagascar" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
and once on 
<collectingRegion box="[1050,1156,1641,1667]" country="Comoros" name="Anjouan" pageId="3" pageNumber="58">Anjouan</collectingRegion>
in the 
<collectingCountry box="[151,253,1395,1421]" name="Comoros" pageId="4" pageNumber="59">Comores</collectingCountry>
. The leaf is dull green on the upper side with three main rose-pink veins, the lower surface is red-purple.
</paragraph>
